          <h2><a name="TOC-The-purpose-of-the-Change-theme"></a>The purpose of the Change theme</h2>
          <div></div>
          <div class="sites-codeblock sites-codesnippet-block">
            <div><code>The purpose of the Change theme is to identify, assess and control any potential and approved changes to the baseline.</code></div>
